spec: agent-core.ai-docs/v1
namespace: DependencyInjection
fqcn: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\DependencyInjection"
updatedAt: 2026-04-19
description: "Symfony bundle extension: config tree definition, config validation, service loading, and framework config prepend (messenger, doctrine)."
files[2]{file,type,summary}:
  Configuration.php,final class,"This class serves as the configuration entry point for the Agent Core dependency injection component, defining the structure of the application's configuration schema. It utilizes Symfony's Config component to build a hierarchical tree that validates and normalizes configuration values."
  AgentLoopExtension.php,final class,This class extends Symfony's Extension to configure the AgentLoop bundle within the dependency injection container. It registers the bundle's configuration schema and loads the associated service definitions. The class acts as the bridge between bundle configuration files and the application's service container.